Comment: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(OP)
Comment: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.32,0:00:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So you're from Mistral?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.58,0:00:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a boring place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:00:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the food there sure is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:00:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are lots of beautiful gals too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been half a year since the truce.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be glad we've managed to survive in one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I win again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.82,0:01:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you win again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:12.36,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that's bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.70,0:01:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey missy, you awake there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.40,0:01:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your share of the winnings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.91,0:01:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Caramel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.42,0:01:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you for giving me such an expensive gift...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.50,0:01:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.05,0:01:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing. They say if we treat the bugler nicely,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be able to hear the calls for retreat loud and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, there's no conscription anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's rare to see a new recruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you volunteer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.64,0:01:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! It's because I wanted to learn music.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.15,0:01:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honesty is a good thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work hard, missy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Second Class, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:01:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Sorami Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:22.54,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}kono sora no kagayaki kimi no mune ni todoiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:22.54,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}The luminance of the sky has reached your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:32.57,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}yumemiteta shirabe wa shizukesa no youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:32.57,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}The melody I dreamed of was like silence.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.44,0:02:37.62,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}kimi no te ga mada yume ni tookutemo
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.44,0:02:37.62,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Even if your hand is still far away in my dreams,
Dialogue: 2,0:02:37.46,0:02:42.68,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}omoidashiteyou yasashii koe wo
Dialogue: 2,0:02:37.46,0:02:42.68,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I'll still remember your kind voice
Dialogue: 3,0:02:42.44,0:02:55.47,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}dareka ga kimi no tame utatta shiawase no koto
Dialogue: 3,0:02:42.44,0:02:55.47,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}and the happiness that was sung for you.
Dialogue: 4,0:02:55.21,0:03:04.87,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}sora no woto hibike takaku kanashimi wo koete
Dialogue: 4,0:02:55.21,0:03:04.87,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Let the sound of the sky ring high over your sadness.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.64,0:03:15.42,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}kimi no me ni utsuru mono wa subete hontou no sekai
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.64,0:03:15.42,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Everything reflected in your eyes is that of the real world.
Dialogue: 6,0:03:15.25,0:03:24.89,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}namida sae kimi wo koko ni todomete okenai
Dialogue: 6,0:03:15.25,0:03:24.89,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Even tears won't be able to stop you here.
Dialogue: 7,0:03:24.62,0:03:37.02,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}furisosogu hikari no naka ashita wo kanadete
Dialogue: 7,0:03:24.62,0:03:37.02,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Amidst the descending lights, you'll play the song of tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:51.31,Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,138)}The Resounding Sound{might as well stay consistent with the rest of the ep and use "resonate" instead of "resound" - Sounds great}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:51.31,Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,621)}The Town of Dawn{This is correct, possessive}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seize is having a festival today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is as far as I can take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is your newly assigned post.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's commonly known as the Time-Trumpeting Fort.{Ok, so I like this title, only because of it's double-meaning. Plus Trumpeting = Announcing/Heralding/Telling/etc. If you don't like it... we can still go with "The Time-Heralding/Telling/Keeping Fort" I guess...}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are to go there yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Notice of Appointment for Private Second Class Sorami Kanata:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are hereby assigned to the 1121st Platoon stationed in Seize, Trois State.{Makes no sense for Trois State to be in front of Seize when a couple of lines down, Konata calls it a town.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As ordered by the Republic of Helvetia's Central Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission accomplished at 1320!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The famous town of water and glass, Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm supposed to report in at 1500.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finally be able to make you sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confirming direction... Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confirming time... Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confirming equipment... Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...march!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-flat... What a beautiful sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10.25 yen. {10 yen, 25 sen equates to this}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a pretty doll—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kitten who was too engrossed in the festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ran full speed in some random direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kittens do like to run around aimlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what makes them cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if it's just a stray.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But unfortunately, this was a house cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That really surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was able to find something else wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's a soldier! Are you from the fort?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for protecting us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sprayed me earlier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot or something?!{Ok... i just have to keep it. I like this >_> - I agree-N}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually getting involved... {Fixed-N}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do looking like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the temperature?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really was an easy target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you even dodge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. This kind of dye disappears on its own once you dry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the festival event, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from a legend in Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the Flame Maidens who protected this town. { or maidens, or "protect" jajajaja}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for troubling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the repairs are finished as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That meddlesome girl...{ok... "Felicia" should be a girl's name you know... >_>}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's late! She's so late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so freaking late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we came all the way here just to welcome her too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But let's continue to wait, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this a gift from your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done. Thank you very much for your hospitality!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but I'm always getting lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to that, I was able to meet such wonderful people!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't get lost out here, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can recognize notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very clear and yet somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...very nostalgic sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't what I—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.61,0:11:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to throw your life away for that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. It's probably meant to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to do so I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it was precious to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward march!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:27.74,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Do you want to see things developed by your voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:34.96,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Do you want to see a purer air, a world with the changed hearts of men?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:42.09,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}But everything on the Earth is fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:48.89,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Nothing is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:07.03,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}When all is said and done, reality is not always mirrored in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flame Maidens?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A very long time ago...
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.82,0:14:14.04,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Which to others, see horrid and demonic things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a story from before the world became the way it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deep within the bowels of the town,
Dialogue: 2,0:14:13.87,0:14:19.54,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}No matter whose story you hear,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dwelt a winged demon.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:19.33,0:14:26.63,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}only your eyes can tell the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That demon spewed flames that made the ground tremble,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:35.31,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}We'll sing the world's colors
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and caused the people to suffer greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, the demon snatched up all the maidens that lived in the fort,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:42.73,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}and not forget a single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and imprisoned them within an underground labyrinth.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.52,0:14:48.95,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Everything has a reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the maidens did not give up.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:48.74,0:14:59.12,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}like the stars in the symphony of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the heavenly gift they had received, they called upon each other with the golden horn...{I think it makes sense to be plural here, i.e. multiple Golden Horns. TLC can check >_> - Certainly makes more sense in English-N}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and finally escaped the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the aid of a giant spider,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they defeated the demon and beheaded it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:10.97,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Everyone makes a song of the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the head continued to spew flames.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.76,0:15:18.02,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Everything is taught and bound.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing was done,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the village below would soon turn to ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to stop the flames,
Dialogue: 2,0:15:17.85,0:15:24.19,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}When we see each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the maidens took turns embracing the demon's head.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:23.98,0:15:31.36,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}we'll become one with the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the demon's head continued to blaze in the maidens' arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the villagers doused them both with water every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It went on for an entire year,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until the flame finally died out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henceforth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to thank the maidens in Heaven who had sacrificed their lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Water-Dousing Festival came to be.{Ok, she says "matsuri", which is festival, and I think she's referring to the festival itself.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, the new girl didn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, hurry up and look! It's Rio-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really suits her well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving her this job was indeed a good decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't we draw lots to—{they weren't exactly straws. the proper phrase is "lots" although i hope people understand that one... otherwise we could go back to "straws"}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to have fun when I got lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was because I was able to meet some nice strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see my mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish for it from the bottom of your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your thoughts will definitely reach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Sound will resound.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will resound...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it will resound...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be conveyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May the Flame Maidens here be at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Embracing the demon and nullifying its curse,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they offered themselves, so that the demon would never awaken again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of a golden horn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me the demon has awakened!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... let my sound... reach someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It reached.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resounds... and will...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and wake up! Private Sorami Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where am I?{Japanese say "this place is", English say "Where am I"... meh....}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When are you going to wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Time-Trumpeting Fort,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the post of the 1121st Platoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday... um... Sorry for causing you trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't endanger yourself like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing all that for this stupid bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trumpet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why this place is known as the Time-Trumpeting Fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the sound of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazumiya Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will teach you how to be a good bugler.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sergeant Major Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Filicia's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Commander's desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:21:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't go by rank here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Rio-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's start right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Play me a morning call right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl this time seems to be very lacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:47.38,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Let's remember our love and friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:47.38,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}aijou yuujou omoikasanete
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.26,0:22:50.59,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}and play out their importance.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.26,0:22:50.59,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}taisetsu wo kanadeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:08.53,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}We were so happy that we cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:08.53,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}ureshikute naita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:14.53,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}It hurt so much that we laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:14.53,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}itakute waratta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:23.71,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}But these are all proof that we are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:23.71,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}dakedo sonna zenbu ga ikiteru akashi nan desu
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.42,0:23:28.05,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Let's move forward one step at a time.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.42,0:23:28.05,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}yukkuri aruite yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:29.51,EDRE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Everybody singing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:34.01,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Let me hear the words of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:34.01,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}hitosashi no honne kikasete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:35.22,EDRE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:40.89,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Even if our love and friendship sometimes waver,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:40.89,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}aijou yuujou toki ni yuretemo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:41.19,EDRE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}I know, you know, a little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:46.82,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}let's make it echo forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:46.82,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}zutto zutto hibiki aitai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:47.19,EDRE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.90,0:23:53.16,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Words are hardly enough to describe it.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:46.90,0:23:53.16,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}arifureteru kotoba de wa tsutaekirenai
Dialogue: 1,0:23:52.86,0:23:58.95,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}This is our harmony.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:52.86,0:23:58.95,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}watashitachi no harmony
Dialogue: 2,0:23:58.87,0:24:04.00,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Can you hear it? Our harmony!
Dialogue: 3,0:23:58.87,0:24:04.00,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}kikoeru our harmony
